main event: Three or four unidentified objects were observed hovering over Lakewood, Arkansas, before moving away.
interesting points: The objects were observed for approximately 15 minutes at a high altitude., They appeared white or gray in color., The objects made an abrupt turn and disappeared from view., There was no physical evidence or photographs captured., The Air Force investigator could not identify the objects based on the limited information.
witness description: The witness observed the objects from their backyard but could provide no further details regarding size or shape.
